<item>
            <title>[STORM-2716] Storm-webapp tests don&apos;t work on Windows</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-2716</link>
                <project id="12314820" key="STORM">Apache Storm</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Several storm-webapp tests don&apos;t work on Windows because file paths like &quot;/tmp&quot; are used, and paths are sometimes constructed by String concatenation instead of using Path.resolve. The logviewer also doesn&apos;t seem to work on Windows, probably for the same reason.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think there might be a few similar issues in other parts of the code, which I&apos;d like to also fix as part of this. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I haven&apos;t checked whether this is a problem in 1.x, but it&apos;s likely.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
